_sText:
Hey guys! It's the second version of the glasstowers map... And what I did? Actually pretty much a lot because the previous map was 3,25MB and this one is 5MB... anyways I played on the first version in a couple of servers and I wasn't so excited because people were abusing spawn shots (u could see another spawn far away from your spawn) anyways so what I did is:

- Anti-spawn shots 
- Moved spawns
- Added two more little towers
- Added HDR
- Changed some little things (added nades on top of towers etc.)
- Improved Gameplay
- Gave some more screenshots (like someone wated before)

I hope you enjoy it!

Darven

*EDIT* All the little holes in the map has been fixed and the file has been uploaded so for all of you who wants to use in on a server just re download it
